ZH: 我们嫁鸡随鸡，搬到他的家乡。
EN: We followed the rooster and moved to his hometown.
ZH: 姐妹们经常嫁鸡随鸡，支持彼此的事业。
EN: Sisters often follow their husbands and support each other's careers.
ZH: 好朋友之间嫁鸡随鸡，一起度过生活的每个阶段。
EN: Good friends follow their husbands and go through every stage of life together.
ZH: 嫁鸡随鸡是我们家族的传统。
EN: Following the husband is a tradition in our family.
ZH: 妻子要会嫁鸡随鸡，尊重丈夫的决定。
EN: A wife should know how to follow her husband and respect his decisions.
ZH: 她跟随丈夫的决定，嫁鸡随鸡地搬到外地工作。
EN: She followed her husband's decision and moved to work in another city.
ZH: 媳妇嫁鸡随鸡，学会适应新的生活环境。
EN: The daughter-in-law followed her husband and learned to adapt to the new living environment.
ZH: 我认为嫁鸡随鸡是一个妻子的责任。
EN: I believe that following the husband is a wife's duty.
ZH: 在我们的文化中，嫁鸡随鸡是理所当然的。
EN: In our culture, it is natural to follow the husband.
ZH: 女性的角色就是嫁鸡随鸡，照顾家庭。
EN: The role of women is to follow their husbands and take care of the family.
ZH: 她选择嫁鸡随鸡，支持丈夫的事业发展。
EN: She chose to follow her husband and support his career development.
ZH: 他们嫁鸡随鸡，一起经营家庭生意。
EN: They followed each other and together managed the family business.
ZH: 忠实的妻子会嫁鸡随鸡，无论丈夫去哪里。
EN: A faithful wife will follow her husband, no matter where he goes.
ZH: 她决定嫁鸡随鸡，不轻言离开家人。
EN: She decided to follow her husband and not leave her family lightly.
ZH: 嫁鸡随鸡不仅仅是迁就，更是为了团聚的家庭之爱。
EN: Following the husband is not just about compromise, but also about the love of a reunited family.
ZH: 她从小就听说嫁鸡随鸡的故事，所以她抱着同样的心态。
EN: She has heard stories of following the husband since she was young, so she holds the same mentality.
ZH: 这个家庭世世代代都是嫁鸡随鸡的传统。
EN: Following the husband is a tradition passed down from generation to generation in this family.
ZH: 我们的婚姻是基于尊重与嫁鸡随鸡的原则建立的。
EN: Our marriage is built on the principles of respect and following the husband.
ZH: 她没有选择嫁鸡随鸡，有时候她觉得孤独。
EN: She didn't choose to follow her husband, and sometimes she feels lonely.
ZH: 嫁鸡随鸡是其中之一的老婆的义务。
EN: Following the husband is one of the duties of a wife.
